1
00:00:14,190 --> 00:00:15,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm Suzume.</i></font>

2
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:18,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm a maid who serves 
at a mansion in the UK.</i></font>

3
00:00:19,720 --> 00:00:21,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However...</i></font>

4
00:00:21,420 --> 00:00:24,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Due to various circumstances, 
said mansion has collapsed.</i></font>

5
00:00:28,310 --> 00:00:30,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font size="30"><font color="#3d1e19">EEK!</font></font></font></font>

6
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:37,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Until it's repaired,</i></font>

7
00:00:37,770 --> 00:00:41,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll be staying here in Japan 
for the next year!</i></font>

8
00:00:43,230 --> 00:00:44,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Done!</font>

9
00:00:51,030 --> 00:00:53,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What shall I have today?</i></font>

10
00:02:40,150 --> 00:02:41,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#929364"><font size="12">CHYUN GUIDE
<font color="#96979b">ALL OF JAPAN</font></font></font></font></font>

11
00:02:41,770 --> 00:02:44,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"One of the highlights of Japan in June..."</font>

12
00:02:44,220 --> 00:02:46,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Hydrangeas glistening 
in the rain are a must-see."</font>

13
00:02:51,830 --> 00:02:53,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#43241e">GRIN</font></font></b></font>

14
00:03:09,020 --> 00:03:10,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#97837f">SILENCE...</font></font></font>

15
00:03:11,110 --> 00:03:12,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

16
00:03:20,650 --> 00:03:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#3c2018">BUMMED</font></b></font></font>

17
00:03:20,650 --> 00:03:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#3c2018">OUT</font></b></font></font>

18
00:03:23,170 --> 00:03:25,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm still heading toward the park...</i></font>

19
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But if there's no rain,
 should I just come back another time?</i></font>

20
00:03:30,100 --> 00:03:35,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="10"><font color="#711fad">HYDRANGEA
<font size="14"><font color="#4246a6">SOFT SERVE</font></font></font></font></font></font>

21
00:03:30,620 --> 00:03:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do I walk to the park or go home?</i></font>

22
00:03:34,090 --> 00:03:36,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need a pick-me-up to make up my mind...</i></font>

23
00:03:35,610 --> 00:03:36,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#df00f0">HYDRANGEA</font></font></font>

24
00:03:36,610 --> 00:03:39,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="10"><font color="#711fad">HYDRANGEA
<font size="14"><font color="#4246a6">SOFT SERVE</font></font></font></font></font></font>

25
00:03:37,510 --> 00:03:38,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A pick-me-up...</i></font>

26
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hydrangea soft serve!</i></font>

27
00:03:41,380 --> 00:03:42,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="36"><font face="Arial Black">{\an8}<font color="#50332a">BAM</font></font></font></font>

28
00:03:46,820 --> 00:03:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's try it!</font>

29
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:55,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I get a gentle, sweet-yet-tangy 
aroma that's oh-so-luxurious.</i></font>

30
00:03:55,780 --> 00:03:57,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With a tartness like blueberries...</i></font>

31
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:03,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="18"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#41221a">IS THIS BLUEBERRY?!</font></font></font></b></font>

32
00:03:59,190 --> 00:04:03,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, is this really blueberry
flavored and not hydrangea?</i></font>

33
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:04,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chyun!</font>

34
00:04:04,660 --> 00:04:09,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The flowers and leaves of hydrangeas 
are toxic, so they're not edible!</font>

35
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is why "hydrangea" flavors</font>

36
00:04:12,540 --> 00:04:15,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are often created using 
blueberries or sweet potatoes.</font>

37
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:17,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As long as it's delicious, 
that's fine by me!</i></font>

38
00:04:17,610 --> 00:04:18,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chyun...</font>

39
00:04:19,460 --> 00:04:24,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, ice cream is sold frozen 
at -18 degrees Celsius or lower,</font>

40
00:04:24,770 --> 00:04:28,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">while soft serve is sold at 
around -5 to -7 degrees Celsius!</font>

41
00:04:28,540 --> 00:04:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not as firm as ice cream, and it's
 known for its light, creamy texture.</font>

42
00:04:36,470 --> 00:04:39,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The toasty, crispy cone 
and the cold soft-serve ice cream...</i></font>

43
00:04:40,340 --> 00:04:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They pair so perfectly. It's delightful!</i></font>

44
00:04:44,300 --> 00:04:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Look at this fanciness
 hidden by the paper!</i></font>

45
00:04:48,650 --> 00:04:51,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder what color 
actual hydrangeas are.</i></font>

46
00:05:08,410 --> 00:05:11,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The color is a lot deeper
than the soft serve earlier.</font>

47
00:05:11,580 --> 00:05:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Almost like the color of wine!</font>

48
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:29,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm glad I came.</i></font>

49
00:05:32,530 --> 00:05:34,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="30"><font color="#261b1c">THE NEXT DAY</font></font></font></font>

50
00:05:34,730 --> 00:05:37,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#929364"><font size="16">CHYUN GUIDE
<font color="#96979b">ALL OF JAPAN</font></font></font></font></font>

51
00:05:37,590 --> 00:05:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there's a dead body buried under 
a hydrangea, it blooms blue?!</font>

52
00:05:41,370 --> 00:05:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So if you see a blue hydrangea...</font>

53
00:05:43,670 --> 00:05:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's true that the color of the flowers
is influenced by soil composition,</font>

54
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:50,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but with selective breeding nowadays,
you can't really generalize...</font>

55
00:05:50,590 --> 00:05:52,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to go see them, but now I'm scared!</font>

56
00:05:53,220 --> 00:05:55,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chyun, chyun! Did you hear what I said?</font>

57
00:06:12,540 --> 00:06:14,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was the last one.</i></font>

58
00:06:17,730 --> 00:06:20,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Remove the stems and wash the plums.</i></font>

59
00:06:20,550 --> 00:06:22,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wipe them with a clean cloth.</i></font>

60
00:06:23,210 --> 00:06:25,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In a heat-sterilized storage jug,</i></font>

61
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>alternate adding plums and rock sugar.</i></font>

62
00:06:32,150 --> 00:06:33,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like layers in the earth.</i></font>

63
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then finally, pour 
clear liquor over the top, and...</i></font>

64
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The plum wine is done!</i></font>

65
00:06:42,650 --> 00:06:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="36">{\an8}<font color="#3e1f18"><b>TA-DA</b></font></font></font></font>

66
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:46,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait to try it.</font>

67
00:06:46,510 --> 00:06:48,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandma should be back any minute.</font>

68
00:06:49,420 --> 00:06:51,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home.</font>

69
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back—</font>

70
00:06:52,910 --> 00:06:54,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, hello, Suzume.</font>

71
00:06:54,140 --> 00:06:55,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ricotta-chan!</font>

72
00:06:55,980 --> 00:06:58,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for taking care of things 
and getting it all set up.</font>

73
00:06:58,740 --> 00:07:01,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bumped into Ricotta just now.</font>

74
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She came by to say hello.</font>

75
00:07:03,290 --> 00:07:04,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

76
00:07:04,700 --> 00:07:07,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Great! Suzume is here too!</i></font>

77
00:07:07,140 --> 00:07:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ricotta-chan?</font>

78
00:07:08,860 --> 00:07:10,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're visiting as well, Suzume?</font>

79
00:07:10,530 --> 00:07:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! I'm here to help make plum wine.</font>

80
00:07:13,330 --> 00:07:14,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Speaking of!</font>

81
00:07:14,330 --> 00:07:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just finished prepping it.</font>

82
00:07:16,580 --> 00:07:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to try some, Ricotta-chan?</font>

83
00:07:18,350 --> 00:07:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't be ready for another six months.</font>

84
00:07:23,470 --> 00:07:26,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Head Maid, this is just 
a small token from me...</font>

85
00:07:26,170 --> 00:07:28,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm now the <i>former</i> head maid.</font>

86
00:07:28,530 --> 00:07:32,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will always be the head maid to me.</font>

87
00:07:33,230 --> 00:07:34,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, thank you.</font>

88
00:07:34,540 --> 00:07:38,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, you could've stayed with us
 instead of renting a place by the month.</font>

89
00:07:38,030 --> 00:07:40,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, that would be asking too much.</font>

90
00:07:40,380 --> 00:07:43,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, do come over anytime.</font>

91
00:07:43,110 --> 00:07:46,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you. I'd love to visit again.</font>

92
00:07:46,710 --> 00:07:47,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzume.</font>

93
00:07:48,900 --> 00:07:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzume!</font>

94
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have plum wine we started last year,
so please serve some to our guest.</font>

95
00:07:54,820 --> 00:07:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We do?!</font>

96
00:07:56,190 --> 00:07:58,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Head Maid, it's still only noon.</font>

97
00:07:58,930 --> 00:08:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plum wine is good for you, so it's okay.</font>

98
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:04,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plum wine has medicinal value
in traditional herbal practices,</font>

99
00:08:04,610 --> 00:08:05,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and is supposedly good before meals!</font>

100
00:08:05,970 --> 00:08:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, it's still alcohol,
 so don't overdo it!</font>

101
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:09,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chyun!</font>

102
00:08:09,580 --> 00:08:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you get it? The jug is in the 
back of the kitchen cupboard.</font>

103
00:08:11,590 --> 00:08:14,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hooray!</font>

104
00:08:15,490 --> 00:08:16,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="36">{\an8}<font color="#3e1f18"><b>TUNK</b></font></font></font></font>

105
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It smells wonderful.</font>

106
00:08:22,070 --> 00:08:24,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rock sugar has all disappeared.</font>

107
00:08:24,410 --> 00:08:25,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the plums are all wrinkly.</font>

108
00:08:28,810 --> 00:08:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait a minute. Are you 
two old enough to drink?</font>

109
00:08:32,730 --> 00:08:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The drinking age is eighteen,
so we're good!</font>

110
00:08:35,410 --> 00:08:37,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that's in the UK.</font>

111
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ricotta, take that away from her.</font>

112
00:08:40,730 --> 00:08:42,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At once.</font>

113
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:45,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have this instead.</font>

114
00:08:46,010 --> 00:08:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plum syrup soda!</font>

115
00:08:49,490 --> 00:08:51,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, now at last...</font>

116
00:08:51,580 --> 00:08:52,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A toast!</font>

117
00:08:52,590 --> 00:08:53,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

118
00:08:57,550 --> 00:08:59,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The richness and aroma 
of the plums are incredible.</font>

119
00:08:59,940 --> 00:09:01,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's delicious.</font>

120
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed, it came out well.</font>

121
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:05,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The plum syrup is nice
 and refreshing as well!</font>

122
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:10,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In any case, I never expected 
you'd come to Japan too, Ricotta.</font>

123
00:09:10,030 --> 00:09:12,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was on the master's orders.</font>

124
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She brought me my summer outfits.</font>

125
00:09:15,050 --> 00:09:17,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We also had biscuits together!</font>

126
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:18,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh my.</font>

127
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:22,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ricotta-chan, do come over
 for biscuits again.</font>

128
00:09:22,090 --> 00:09:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be waiting!</font>

129
00:09:23,290 --> 00:09:26,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sure... When I feel like it.</font>

130
00:09:26,530 --> 00:09:27,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When will that be?</font>

131
00:09:27,620 --> 00:09:29,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As I said, when I feel like it.</font>

132
00:09:30,070 --> 00:09:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When do you think you'll feel like it?</font>

133
00:09:31,830 --> 00:09:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gosh, you're being pushy, Suzume!</font>

134
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, then I'll see you tomorrow!</font>

135
00:09:40,770 --> 00:09:42,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't know until tomorrow.</font>

136
00:09:43,380 --> 00:09:45,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great, I'll be expecting you!</font>

137
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:50,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The plum wine you just prepared, Suzume...</font>

138
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:53,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't we save it until 
you're old enough to drink?</font>

139
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:55,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll keep that long?</font>

140
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:56,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chyun!</font>

141
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:58,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Depending on how it's stored,</font>

142
00:09:58,450 --> 00:10:01,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">homemade plum wine can 
be kept for about a decade.</font>

143
00:10:01,450 --> 00:10:06,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both of you come back when 
you're of age, all right?</font>

144
00:10:06,290 --> 00:10:08,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-Both of us?!</font>

145
00:10:08,110 --> 00:10:08,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

146
00:10:08,740 --> 00:10:09,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

147
00:10:09,530 --> 00:10:10,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I...</font>

148
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:13,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ricotta, calm down.</font>

149
00:10:13,780 --> 00:10:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Head Maid!</font>

150
00:10:15,550 --> 00:10:18,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#41251e"><b>THAT WAS DELICIOUS!</b></font></font></font>

151
00:10:25,810 --> 00:10:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! That takes care 
of my errand for Grandma.</font>

152
00:10:56,220 --> 00:10:59,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rainy season is over, and we've
 now entered summer in Japan.</font>

153
00:11:01,410 --> 00:11:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, right! Grandma sent me off 
with this when I left the house.</i></font>

154
00:11:17,940 --> 00:11:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barley tea in a thermos!</font>

155
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It sounds like a gentle bell...</i></font>

156
00:11:24,190 --> 00:11:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like treasure!</i></font>

157
00:11:27,390 --> 00:11:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But why?</i></font>

158
00:11:35,550 --> 00:11:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's try it!</font>

159
00:11:41,090 --> 00:11:44,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barley tea is made with roasted barley!</font>

160
00:11:44,570 --> 00:11:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since it's caffeine-free,
 it makes a nice drink any time!</font>

161
00:12:07,330 --> 00:12:09,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, there's ice!</font>

162
00:12:09,390 --> 00:12:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Can I just get the ice somehow?</i></font>

163
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ah, it's not coming out.</i></font>

164
00:12:15,590 --> 00:12:16,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it!</font>

165
00:12:22,460 --> 00:12:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The clinking of ice and cicadas crying...</i></font>

166
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:28,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It doesn't get more summery than this!</i></font>

167
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:41,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That math mini quiz was totally nuts!</font>

168
00:12:41,820 --> 00:12:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yujiro!</font>

169
00:12:44,380 --> 00:12:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to talk to you... 
about something.</font>

170
00:12:57,330 --> 00:12:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I got here too early.</i></font>

171
00:12:59,690 --> 00:13:02,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I hope everything goes okay.</i></font>

172
00:13:02,010 --> 00:13:04,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? How do you ask for someone's name?</font>

173
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:07,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of question is that?</font>

174
00:13:07,750 --> 00:13:11,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know where to start...</font>

175
00:13:11,140 --> 00:13:14,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I figured I'd only ask the question 
at hand to keep it brief.</font>

176
00:13:14,430 --> 00:13:15,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need a little more context.</font>

177
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, can't you just ask normally...?</font>

178
00:13:20,450 --> 00:13:21,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

179
00:13:22,210 --> 00:13:24,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#695358">BEAM</font></b></font></font>

180
00:13:23,420 --> 00:13:24,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

181
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:28,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. You've already reached
 that point, eh, Sora?</font>

182
00:13:28,740 --> 00:13:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop making that face!</font>

183
00:13:30,610 --> 00:13:33,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm anxious... Terribly anxious.</i></font>

184
00:13:34,050 --> 00:13:34,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me.</font>

185
00:13:36,290 --> 00:13:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry to keep you waiting.</font>

186
00:13:38,430 --> 00:13:40,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's really here!</i></font>

187
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:43,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I positively had to thank you
 for your help.</font>

188
00:13:45,220 --> 00:13:48,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're probably starting to 
get heatstroke, so drink this.</font>

189
00:13:48,940 --> 00:13:51,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I appreciate your thoughtfulness, 
but this is all I need.</font>

190
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:51,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm okay—</font>

191
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:53,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please just drink it!</font>

192
00:13:53,630 --> 00:13:55,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#422118">STARE</font></b></font></font></font>

193
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:57,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

194
00:14:00,460 --> 00:14:02,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you bought those drinks for me,</font>

195
00:14:02,500 --> 00:14:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if I didn't return the favor,
my grandmother would be cross with me.</font>

196
00:14:07,010 --> 00:14:10,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for taking the time
 to meet up like this.</font>

197
00:14:10,100 --> 00:14:13,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really, it's fine. I'm just 
glad that you're okay.</font>

198
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mission: Ask for her name!</i></font>

199
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial">{\an7}<font color="#452622"><b>ASK FOR HER NAME</b></font></font></font>

200
00:14:16,410 --> 00:14:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what... what's your...</font>

201
00:14:19,290 --> 00:14:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't just ask out of the blue.</i></font>

202
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>First, get a conversation 
going by talking about</i></font>

203
00:14:23,870 --> 00:14:26,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the weather or complimenting her outfit!</i></font>

204
00:14:26,170 --> 00:14:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your outfit... That's a maid uniform.</font>

205
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:37,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="20"><font color="#462421">JUST A THOUGHT</font></font></font></font>

206
00:14:30,510 --> 00:14:31,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yikes!</i></font>

207
00:14:31,890 --> 00:14:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yes. But it's lighter than 
the one I was wearing before!</font>

208
00:14:35,490 --> 00:14:37,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I see.</font>

209
00:14:37,560 --> 00:14:44,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#402015">THA-THUMP THA-THUMP</font></font></font>

210
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:41,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, how do you compliment a maid outfit?</i></font>

211
00:14:41,110 --> 00:14:43,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't have that kind of experience yet!</i></font>

212
00:14:43,030 --> 00:14:44,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What about the weather?!</i></font>

213
00:14:44,540 --> 00:14:47,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been hot lately, hasn't it?</font>

214
00:14:48,900 --> 00:14:53,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm afraid that's why
 I was such a burden last time.</font>

215
00:14:53,400 --> 00:14:56,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm very sorry for putting you
 through all of that.</font>

216
00:14:56,170 --> 00:14:58,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So please enjoy these with your family.</font>

217
00:14:58,860 --> 00:15:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Th-This isn't going anywhere...</i></font>

218
00:15:04,330 --> 00:15:05,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A maid's intuition!</i></font>

219
00:15:05,930 --> 00:15:06,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon...</font>

220
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:09,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're thinking about crepes, yes?</font>

221
00:15:10,420 --> 00:15:11,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

222
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:16,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, right. There's a crepe shop 
across the way.</i></font>

223
00:15:16,100 --> 00:15:19,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I totally understand. It can be 
nerve-racking to try a new place.</font>

224
00:15:19,470 --> 00:15:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, um... I...</font>

225
00:15:22,030 --> 00:15:24,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be fine if we go together.</font>

226
00:15:24,070 --> 00:15:25,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So let us be off!</font>

227
00:15:28,020 --> 00:15:29,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess that's fine.</i></font>

228
00:15:34,890 --> 00:15:36,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do I ask her name now?</i></font>

229
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:38,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe it's not the right time.</i></font>

230
00:15:41,830 --> 00:15:43,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's so excited.</i></font>

231
00:15:48,070 --> 00:15:49,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do I ask now?</i></font>

232
00:15:50,950 --> 00:15:53,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then, let's eat!</font>

233
00:15:57,910 --> 00:16:01,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My head's so full of thoughts, 
I can't even taste this crepe.</i></font>

234
00:16:01,310 --> 00:16:02,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon, but...</font>

235
00:16:03,820 --> 00:16:05,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is delicious!</font>

236
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:11,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The cream is sweet, 
and the strawberries are tart!</font>

237
00:16:11,650 --> 00:16:14,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The chocolate sauce adds 
a delightful accent!</font>

238
00:16:14,070 --> 00:16:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The thin layers of crepe 
give it a delightful texture too!</font>

239
00:16:17,370 --> 00:16:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's sweet all the way through,</font>

240
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:21,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the experience is so blissful,
 I don't want to stop!</font>

241
00:16:25,500 --> 00:16:26,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good.</font>

242
00:16:28,410 --> 00:16:29,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was delicious.</font>

243
00:16:29,910 --> 00:16:30,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was fast!</font>

244
00:16:30,840 --> 00:16:35,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, do you happen to 
know why they're called crepes?</font>

245
00:16:35,660 --> 00:16:36,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't.</font>

246
00:16:36,730 --> 00:16:38,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She jumps topics a lot...</i></font>

247
00:16:38,870 --> 00:16:39,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chyun!</font>

248
00:16:39,630 --> 00:16:43,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Crepe" comes from a French word
 suggesting silk.</font>

249
00:16:43,290 --> 00:16:46,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They got the name from the pattern 
on their cooked surface,</font>

250
00:16:46,530 --> 00:16:48,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which resembles fabric.</font>

251
00:16:48,650 --> 00:16:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f8f0bd"><font size="12">CHYUN GUIDE
<font color="#fbfbfb">ALL OF JAPAN</font></font></font></font></font>

252
00:16:48,650 --> 00:16:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see! So the origin of the name is...</font>

253
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:53,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, names...</font>

254
00:16:54,050 --> 00:16:55,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me!</font>

255
00:16:55,770 --> 00:16:58,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We haven't really introduced 
ourselves yet, have we?</font>

256
00:16:58,820 --> 00:17:01,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Suzume Tachibana.</font>

257
00:17:01,160 --> 00:17:03,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really wanted to ask yours today!</font>

258
00:17:08,130 --> 00:17:10,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's laughing at me...</i></font>

259
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:12,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Sora Endo.</font>

260
00:17:13,290 --> 00:17:18,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Jeez, I should've just asked her
 from the beginning, like Yujiro said.</i></font>

261
00:17:19,030 --> 00:17:22,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've actually wanted to ask you 
your name all this time too.</font>

262
00:17:24,870 --> 00:17:26,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's nice to know!</font>

263
00:17:26,890 --> 00:17:28,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Endo-san.</font>

264
00:17:28,210 --> 00:17:29,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tachibana-san.</font>

265
00:17:35,500 --> 00:17:36,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this for real?</font>

266
00:17:37,550 --> 00:17:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Sora!</font>

267
00:17:55,410 --> 00:17:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Recently, someone new moved onto my turf.</i></font>

268
00:18:08,520 --> 00:18:13,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This girl in strange clothes is 
eating something yet again today.</i></font>

269
00:18:21,630 --> 00:18:24,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What the heck is it this time?</i></font>

270
00:18:25,950 --> 00:18:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's rice.</i></font>

271
00:18:27,980 --> 00:18:30,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know that's not very good.</i></font>

272
00:18:34,450 --> 00:18:35,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What the heck is that?</i></font>

273
00:18:36,800 --> 00:18:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#422118"><b>LET'S EAT</b></font></font></font>

274
00:18:37,170 --> 00:18:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's eat!</font>

275
00:18:49,730 --> 00:18:51,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Could that be...</i></font>

276
00:18:51,690 --> 00:18:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>something tasty?</i></font>

277
00:18:55,190 --> 00:18:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raw egg over rice became 
popular in early Meiji times</font>

278
00:18:57,570 --> 00:19:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when a certain journalist began 
eating it and spread the idea!</font>

279
00:19:01,030 --> 00:19:05,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eggs used to be a luxury item, so people 
didn't have them often back then.</font>

280
00:19:05,860 --> 00:19:08,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, rather than soy sauce,</font>

281
00:19:08,390 --> 00:19:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they were seasoned with salt 
or chili peppers back then!</font>

282
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:14,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't that make you want to try it?</font>

283
00:19:15,020 --> 00:19:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's savoring every bite.</i></font>

284
00:19:17,620 --> 00:19:19,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It must be really good.</i></font>

285
00:19:20,470 --> 00:19:23,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shoot! The second time 
she strikes that pose...</i></font>

286
00:19:24,370 --> 00:19:26,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew it! She ate it all!</i></font>

287
00:19:30,850 --> 00:19:31,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Give me some!</i></font>

288
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:35,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I prefer the canned stuff,
 but that will do!</i></font>

289
00:19:40,230 --> 00:19:41,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning.</font>

290
00:19:41,590 --> 00:19:44,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll deign to eat the same food as you.</i></font>

291
00:19:44,950 --> 00:19:48,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. I can't give you any rice.</font>

292
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:52,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can sense she's holding out on me.</i></font>

293
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:55,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hey, girl in the strange clothes!</i></font>

294
00:19:55,220 --> 00:19:57,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Make sure you have something 
for me next time.</i></font>

295
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:59,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Got that?</i></font>

296
00:19:59,800 --> 00:20:01,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hey, did you get that?</i></font>

297
00:20:01,650 --> 00:20:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You better have something for me!</i></font>

298
00:20:05,090 --> 00:20:06,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How cute.</font>

299
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:21,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should really take it inside now...</font>

300
00:20:21,530 --> 00:20:23,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this feels too good to move.</font>

301
00:20:26,110 --> 00:20:29,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I have to get to the 
prepared foods store at four!</font>

302
00:20:29,440 --> 00:20:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Here you go. It's freshly made!</i></font>

303
00:20:34,110 --> 00:20:35,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, here we go.</font>

304
00:20:41,690 --> 00:20:43,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That surprised me!</i></font>

305
00:20:44,090 --> 00:20:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm glad the bedding was there...</i></font>

306
00:20:46,790 --> 00:20:50,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Granted, it's what made me trip
 in the first place.</i></font>

307
00:20:56,750 --> 00:20:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It smells like the sun...</i></font>

308
00:21:03,550 --> 00:21:04,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's so nice...</i></font>

309
00:21:27,300 --> 00:21:29,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? I fell asleep...</font>

310
00:21:31,280 --> 00:21:32,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black">{\an8}<font size="36"><font color="#09080f">PITCH BLACK</font></font></font></font>

311
00:21:32,850 --> 00:21:34,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Oh no!</font>

312
00:21:35,090 --> 00:21:36,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's totally dark out!</font>

313
00:21:36,620 --> 00:21:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="20"><font color="#0b070e">GRUMBLE GRUMBLE</font></font></font></font>

314
00:21:39,500 --> 00:21:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I overslept big-time!</font>

315
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:46,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll be waiting for you... I'll be waiting
for you... I'll be waiting for you...</i></font>

316
00:21:49,120 --> 00:21:52,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I missed dinner!</font>

317
00:21:52,630 --> 00:21:56,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's said that naps from fifteen
 to thirty minutes are ideal.</font>

318
00:21:56,990 --> 00:21:58,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's be careful not to oversleep.</font>

319
00:21:58,970 --> 00:22:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chyun!</font>

320
00:23:30,550 --> 00:23:34,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandma always taught me
that summers in Japan are hot,</font>

321
00:23:34,410 --> 00:23:36,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you should eat well and stay strong.</font>

322
00:23:36,260 --> 00:23:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's enjoy the summer 
full of energy from delicious food!</font>

